#X text 55 38 La Tourelle is a interactive sculpture. The interaction is made by the sharing of files : each people can share files to the sculpture. The files are renamed by the C# program in number (like 1.jpg \, 2.pdf \, 3.pd \, ...). Here \, PureData read these files and sonify them. The speaker is a audio transducter on the sculpture. When sound is played \, the sculpture diffuse the sound by vibration. The DataSound is melted to the motor sound of the sculpture., f 83;
